            <title>[LU-16194] Define negative PFL extent start/end as invalid</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16194</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Even though lu_extent.e_start and lu_extent.e_end are u64 type, we convert them to s64 and check whether they are negative values on MDS. All negative values except -1 (EOF) are regarded as invalid.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
